name: Russell Investments Real Assets
longDescription: The Fund investment objective is to provide exposure to a diversified portfolio of asset classes that are directly or indirectly linked to physical assets, or to assets that the investment manager of the fund believes have a tendency to maintain their real (after inflation) value over time. The Fund invests in or gains exposure to primarily equity securities fixed income securities, permitted commodities and securities of other mutual funds.
